and-200 transition\">Handelsbetingelser</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-brand-200 transition\">Cookiepolitik</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"pt-8 border-t border-stone-800 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs font-light text-stone-600\">\n                <p>&copy; 2023 Grynnerup Aesthetics. Registreret hos Styrelsen for Patientsikkerhed.</p>\n                <p class=\"mt-2 md:mt-0\">Designet med fokus på æstetik.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <!-- EasyPractice Booking Script -->\n    <script src=\"https://system.easypractice.net/online_book/onlinebook.js?url=https%3A%2F%2Fsystem.easypractice.net&affix=/book/grynnerup-aesthetics&txt=Book%20en%20tid\" id=\"terapeutbookingonlinebooking\"></script>\n    \n    <script>\n        lucide.createIcons();\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>","language":"html","username":"c9ceb3d9-8f1e-4a2a-8c48-dd4ab7d32b17","created_at":"2026-01-13T11:54:36.833886+00:00","views":194,"image_url":"https://hoirqrkdgbmvpwutwuwj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preview-images/shared-code-previews/grynnerup-aesthetics-preview-1769349935074.jpeg","forks":4,"private":false,"watermark":true,"featured":true,"share_source_code":true,"user_id":"c9ceb3d9-8f1e-4a2a-8c48-dd4ab7d32b17","category":"Web","updated_at":null,"tags":["Landing Page","Health","Services","Brand","Clean","Minimal","Large Type","Cosmetic clinic","Medical aesthetics","Danish"],"description":"A refined aesthetic clinic landing page template for cosmetic treatment providers, featuring services, pricing, FAQs, and booking-focused CTAs.","premium":false,"price":null,"purchase_url":null,"long_description":"**Aesthetic Clinic Landing Page Template**\n\nA premium, Scandinavian-inspired template for cosmetic and aesthetic clinics to showcase treatments, pricing, and easy booking.\n\n## What's Included\n- Hero section with strong value proposition and dual CTAs\n- Philosophy/principles section to build trust and credibility\n- Treatment cards for injectables, fillers, and skinboosters\n- Structured pricing table and FAQ accordion\n- Booking and contact block with address, email, and phone\n\n## Key Features\n- **Clean, minimal, high-end visual style**\n- **Service-focused layout for injectables and skincare**\n- **Clear pricing with categories and notes**\n- **Trust-building copy for safety and natural results**\n- **Mobile-responsive Tailwind CSS structure**\n\n**Primary Use Case:**\nPerfect for aesthetic, cosmetic, and beauty clinics that need a polished landing page to present treatments, communicate pricing, answer common questions, and drive online bookings.","custom_domain":null,"favicon_light_url":null,"favicon_dark_url":null,"dns_verified":null,"dns_verified_at":null,"dns_a_record":null,"netlify_apex_exists":null,"netlify_www_exists":null,"netlify_verified_at":null,"custom_domain_added_at":null,"netlify_site_id":null,"umami_website_id":null,"umami_share_id":null,"analytics_enabled":false,"gtm_container_id":null,"remix_source":{},"credit_remix_source":false,"search_visibility":"aura_and_custom_domain","llms_txt":null,"llms_txt_updated_at":null}]